php5-luasandbox (2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Various Debian packaging fixes
    - Bump to debhelper compatibility level 9
    - Update Standards-Version to 3.9.3
    - Move custom install statements under dh_auto_install to an install file.
    - Add a Homepage field.
    - Reformat debian/copyright to match the new copyright format and to
      clarify that the license is the Expat variant.
    - Add dependency on the phpapi virtual package.
    - Switch to the 3.0 (native) source format.
  * Add an hhvm-luasandbox package and add hacks to build the source twice,
    once for PHP and once for HHVM.

 -- Faidon Liambotis <faidon@wikimedia.org>  Fri, 27 Jun 2014 16:18:05 +0000

